.TH "libnvmf_get_default_trsvcid" 9 "libnvmf_get_default_trsvcid" "April 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
libnvmf_get_default_trsvcid \- Get default transport service ID
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "const char *" libnvmf_get_default_trsvcid
.BI "(const char *transport "  ","
.BI "bool discovery_ctrl "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "transport" 12
Transport type string (e.g., "tcp", "rdma")
.IP "discovery_ctrl" 12
True if for discovery controller, false otherwise
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Returns the default trsvcid (port) for the given transport and controller
type.
.SH "RETURN"
Allocated string with default trsvcid, or NULL on failure.
